0:{"rsc":["$","$1","c",{"children":[["$","$L2",null,{"title":"Cosmo Baseで宇宙知っトク","level":2,"levelTitle":"自分を知る","logo":"CBshittoku","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"glass-card rounded-xl p-8 mb-8","children":["$","div",null,{"className":"flex items-start gap-4 mb-6","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"p-3 rounded-lg bg-primary/20","children":["$","svg",null,{"xmlns":"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg","width":24,"height":24,"viewBox":"0 0 24 24","fill":"none","stroke":"currentColor","strokeWidth":2,"strokeLinecap":"round","strokeLinejoin":"round","className":"lucide lucide-calendar w-8 h-8 text-primary","aria-hidden":"true","children":[["$","path","1cmpym",{"d":"M8 2v4"}],["$","path","4m81vk",{"d":"M16 2v4"}],["$","rect","1hopcy",{"width":"18","height":"18","x":"3","y":"4","rx":"2"}],["$","path","8toen8",{"d":"M3 10h18"}],"$undefined"]}]}],["$","div",null,{"children":[["$","h2",null,{"className":"text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2","children":"「ちょっと気になる」をみんなで楽しむ、気軽な学びの場。"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed space-y-3","children":[["$","p",null,{"children":"宇宙に関するテーマを、分かりやすく楽しく学べる定期イベントです。ニュースの解説やミニ講座、座談会など、毎回さまざまな形式で開催され、専門知識がなくても気軽に参加できます。"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"一方的に話を聞くだけでなく、気になったことをその場で質問したり、他の参加者の意見を聞けたりと、自然な会話が生まれるのが特徴です。「少し知ってみたい」という気持ちがあれば十分楽しめます。"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"毎週水曜日の定期開催により、宇宙に触れる心地よいリズムが生まれます。「知る」だけでなく「話す」「共有する」体験を通じて、宇宙をもっと身近でワクワクするものに変えていきましょう。"}]]}]]}]]}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"mb-8 flex flex-col items-center","children":[["$","h3",null,{"className":"text-lg font-semibold text-foreground mb-4 self-start w-full","children":"今月のイベント"}],["$","div",null,{"className":"w-full max-w-3xl mx-auto rounded-xl overflow-hidden border border-border/50 shadow-md","children":["$","img",null,{"src":"/member_only/_next/static/media/2604.14-57pat7.ovj.jpeg","alt":"今月のイベント","className":"w-full h-auto object-cover transition-transform duration-500"}]}]]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"grid md:g